title: what it’s REALLY like to create a size inclusive brand with alisha marie and ashley nichole
itunes:title: what it’s REALLY like to create a size inclusive brand with alisha marie and ashley nichole
description:
Brooke and Danielle are joined by Alisha Marie and Ashley Nichole to discuss their new brand, Parallel Apparel!   The gals deep dive into the challenges of starting a business, what it is like to work with your sister, and what’s to come with Parallel!  


Check out Parallel Apparel!  https://www.parallelapparel.com/
